title: 042711_AllSurveyPoints
name: 042711_AllSurveyPoints
description: The information contained in this shapefile includes comprehensive storm survey point information depicting several parameters used for surveying storm survey damage, including Survey Date, Damage Indicator (damage_txt), Degree of Damage (dod_txt), EF-Rating, Damage Direction, Wind Speed, Survey Comments, Lattitude and Longitude, Survey Office, and the Tornado associated with a single point.  THE DATA CONTAINED IN THE SHAPEFILE ARE EXPERIMENTAL.
